  "response": "I'll break down typical interview questions for each sector:\n\nResearch & Development Sector:\nTechnical Questions:\n1. Describe your research methodology\n2. What innovative projects have you worked on?\n3. How do you approach problem-solving?\n4. Explain your technical expertise\n5. What research publications have you authored?\n\nBehavioral Questions:\n1. How do you handle project failures?\n2. Describe your collaboration experience\n3. How do you stay updated with latest research trends?\n\nPolymer Industry:\nTechnical Questions:\n1. Explain polymer synthesis techniques\n2. What experience do you have with different polymer types?\n3. Describe material characterization methods\n4. How do you optimize polymer properties?\n5. Discuss polymer processing techniques\n\nBehavioral Questions:\n1. How do you ensure quality control?\n2. Describe your experience with industrial applications\n3. How do you handle technical challenges?\n\nMNC (Multinational Corporation):\nTechnical Questions:\n1. Explain your technical skills\n2. How do you adapt to different technologies?\n3. Describe your project management experience\n4. What software/tools are you proficient in?\n\nBehavioral Questions:\n1. How do you handle cross-cultural teams?\n2. Describe your communication skills\n3. How do you manage work pressure?\n4. What are your long-term career goals?\n\nGeneral Interview Questions:\n1. Tell me about yourself\n2. Why do you want to work here?\n3. What are your strengths/weaknesses?\n4. Where do you see yourself in 5 years?",
